Package: AverageByGroup
Title: Average a numerical variable across a group of categorical variables
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Apsara", "Srinivas", , "apsara.srinivas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains the average_by_group function, which takes in a dataset, and produces a tibble containing calculated averages of a numerical variable, grouped according to a categorical variable. This package is dependent on the tidyverse and dplyr packages. 
